EmailTemplate.subject: Invitation: Explore Year 7 - Tuesday 29 May, 2018
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Lead.FirstName}
I am delighted to invite you and your family to our Explore Year 7 Evening on Tuesday 29 May.
On the evening you will have the opportunity to visit our Middle School campus, take part in taster classes and gain insight into what makes our city school so special.
Listen to keynote speakers and information sessions; Experience fun demonstrations and interactive workshops; Speak with specialty staff and community representatives who will be available to answer your questions; and Enjoy entertainment and a sausage sizzle on our famous Rooftop Playground.
Registration from 5.00pm
Keynote speakers from 5.30pm
Head of School, Dr John Collier speaking at 6.00pm and 7.00pm
Bookings essential.
Please book online via our website
https://www.sacs.nsw.edu.au/book-a-tour/tour-bookings/
I do hope you can join us for this for this very special event.
Regards
John Partington Head of Middle School
St Andrew's Cathedral School
Sydney Square, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia
direct 9286 9552 email RPedley@sacs.nsw.edu.au phone +61 2 9286 9500 fax +61 29286 9550
You are receiving this invitation as you have previously indicated interest in enrolment at St Andrew’s Cathedral School. We would love you to come to along on our Explore Year 7 event however, if you would like to unsubscribe from further invitations, please click here.
